em to meet future business needs. Youâll ensure that data is secure, compliant, discoverable, and business-ready, enabling analysts, data scientists, and stakeholders to make confident, data-driven decisions.&nbsp; This role is ideal for a highly technical leader who thrives at both the strategic and execution levels: someone equally comfortable defining architecture with executives, mentoring senior engineers, and optimising distributed pipelines at scale.&nbsp; 
